ListCurrenciesOutput.example:
<soapenv:Envelope xmlns:soapenv="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/">
 <soapenv:Body>
  <tns:ListCurrenciesResponse xmlns:tns="http://www.xignite.com/services/">
   <tns:ListCurrenciesResult>
    <tns:Outcome><!-- mandatory -->string</tns:Outcome>
    <tns:Message>string</tns:Message>
    <tns:Identity>string</tns:Identity>
    <tns:Delay><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:Delay>
    <tns:Currencies>
     <tns:CurrencyItem><!-- between zero and unlimited repetitions of this element -->
      <tns:Symbol>string</tns:Symbol>
      <tns:Name>string</tns:Name>
      <tns:Plural>string</tns:Plural>
      <tns:Supported><!-- mandatory -->true</tns:Supported>
      <tns:Active><!-- mandatory -->true</tns:Active>
      <tns:ActiveMessage>string</tns:ActiveMessage>
      <tns:Countries>
       <tns:Country><!-- between zero and unlimited repetitions of this element -->
        <tns:Code>string</tns:Code>
        <tns:Name>string</tns:Name>
       </tns:Country>
      </tns:Countries>
     </tns:CurrencyItem>
    </tns:Currencies>
   </tns:ListCurrenciesResult>
  </tns:ListCurrenciesResponse>
 </soapenv:Body>
</soapenv:Envelope>
